# Chemprop nanoHUB Demo

This is the source code for a [nanoHUB tool](https://nanohub.org/tools/chempropdemo) that demonstrates how to use [Chemprop](https://github.com/chemprop/chemprop) within Python (in a Jupyter notebook) using Chemprop v1.4.1.
